title: Pink Floyd - 1977-05-09 - Alameda Stadium in Oakland, CA   AUD
description:
Pink Floyd

1977-05-09

Alameda Stadium

Oakland CA



Audience - 
Pristine sound...It's quite amazing actually.  Best audience Floyd show I've heard.




There are many versions of this show...

Definitive Oakland (Sigma 37) is posted here but there is no confirmed lineage according to the link in the post. I have every version and this is by far superior.
